title: 225. Q&AF: Starting Or Finishing, Technology Taking Over & Creating An Impact

description: In today's episode, Andy answers your questions on what's more important, the start or the finish, whether you should invest in humans or automate the process with technology, and what is something or someone that has contributed to Andy's success.
